ORIGINAL POST ---> http://csgo.gamebanana.com/maps/172068

All credits for the original mapper: Xenosaj

This is meant to be a fun map with plenty of hiding spots and a few hidden secrets. The console tells you what you need to know when the round starts. I tried to make the entire map as balanced as I could for both humans and zombies so that no single hiding spot is too easy to defend. Installation is stupid simple, it's a packed .bsp file that goes in your csgo/maps directory.
